      "role": "user",
      "content": "it doesn't feel like it's just \"hidden\" though. it feels like the artist is genuinely dead. like the spark that made me *me* is just gone. and now i'm just... physics. just skin and bones moving around because of habit. it feels wrong to keep occupying this space when the person who was supposed to live here is already gone.",
